row.Title: Why Polls Missed A Shocker In Virginia’s Senate Race FiveThirtyEight » Nate Silver | FiveThirtyEight
row.Selection: Projections from early exit polls have a well-deserved reputation for being dubious — just ask President John Kerry. But early Tuesday evening, they suggested a potentially shocking outcome in Virginia.
